# Test Coverage Gap Analysis: Kafka Consumer Group Coordinator

## Summary

The Kafka consumer group coordinator manages consumer group membership, partition assignment, and offset commits. Analysis of the test files (`GroupCoordinatorServiceTest.java`, `GroupCoordinatorShardTest.java`, and `GroupMetadataManagerTest.java`) reveals several important failure modes and state transition scenarios that lack dedicated regression tests. These gaps expose the coordinator to potential data loss, incorrect partition assignments, resource leaks, and inconsistent group state transitions during error conditions.

